title: Cherry Goo Does Contortionist School : Naughty Adventure 2
description: Mortified at the unexpected outcome of her last groupie party, the gorgeous but narcissistic Cherry Goo Rock Goddess, decides to take self gratification to an entirely new level.As usual her personal assistant, Max who suffers from unrequited love, is forced to go along for the crazy ride.This time it is contortionist school.Will he ever get a chance with Cherry?Find out in the next naughty adventures of Cherry Goo
author: Savvy Love
